message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL. The paper discusses a framework for analyzing large documents and using machine learning techniques, including deep learning, to identify and classify semantic sections of documents. This falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
